name: Outlet
query:
Select name, current_stock_level__petrol_l AS "Current Petrol Level Litter",current_stock_level__petrol_l/total_capacity_for_petrol * 100 AS "Current Petrol Level" ,
current_stock_level_diesel_l AS "Current Diesel Level Litter",current_stock_level_diesel_l/total_capacity_for_diesel * 100 AS "Current Diesel Level" ,total_capacity_for_petrol AS "Petrol - Total Capacity", 
total_capacity_for_diesel AS "Diesel - Total Capacity"
from tabOutlet
group by name
